    "The editor F4 opens the file under the cursor in. ⇧F4 names a new file first, creating it if it doesn’t exist yet.": {
      "comment": "Operations footer: text editor.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The editor F4 opens the file under the cursor in. ⇧F4 names a new file first, creating it if it doesn’t exist yet."
